    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Hammer Time\r\n\r\nFollow MC Hammer's **algorithm** to recreate parts of Can't Touch This\r\n\r\n1) First you need to stop... because it's hammer time.\r\n2) Then play the main loop with the big beat **twice**\r\n3) Then it's time to Break it Down... because you Can't Touch This\r\n4) Then do the Breakdown tracks **twice**\r\n5) End it strong by saying I Told Ya!\r\n\r\nFollow the **algorithm** to recreate this song! It should sound like the example below!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/5397c925f43256b6b674873e14427f4f-image-1749506942263.png)",
